('01940000-0008-7000-8000-000000000008', 'Graff Pink Diamond Ring 1.8ct Fancy Intense Pink', 'Ultra-rare Graff fancy intense pink diamond ring. Center stone: 1.8 carat radiant-cut natural pink diamond, GIA certified. Surrounded by white diamonds totaling 0.5 carats. Platinum setting. Pink diamonds are among the rarest gemstones in the world. Investment-grade piece with exceptional color saturation.', 'Ring', 680000000, 725000000, 5000000, NULL, NOW() + INTERVAL '10 days', true, 'Active', 18, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605100804763-247f67b3557e', ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601121141461-9d6647bca1ed', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612595989600-d1f8f72c4f0e', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603561591411-07134e71a2a9'], false, '01930000-0004-7000-8000-000000000004', '01930000-0011-7000-8000-000000000011', NOW() - INTERVAL '1 day', NOW()),
